  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DALBackEndServices
    This interface is part of the DAL (Data Access Layer).
    DALServices
    This interface is part of the DAL (Data Access Layer).
    DAO<T>
    This interface exposes the basic CRUD operations performed on the database that are shared by all the DAOs (Data Access Objects).
    ProjectDAO
    Interface for database action regarding projects
    UserDAO
    The UserDAO extends DAO (basic CRUD operations) and can be used to add specific methods related to Users Such as find user by email.
